Customize
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- hover
.coba:hover{ color: red; }
- unselect user supaya kelihatan seperti aplikasi pada elemen webnya
.coba {user-select: none;
  -moz-user-select: none;
  -webkit-user-select: none;
  -ms-user-select: none;}
- input field
form input{
  border: none;
  outline: none;  
}

